Gauffr 0.9 (2011-??-??)
-----------------------
''Realease candidate of the first stable release''
 - Move to GIT.
 - Add GauffrAdmin, the Gauffr WebUI:
  - Can edit credentials,
  - Can edit extended informations,
  - Can read logs,
 - Add an install script.
 - Add an update script.
 - A lot of others enhancements and fixes.

Gauffr 0.4 (2010-08-25)
-----------------------
''The first version usable in production !''

 - New database schema defined by .XML
 - Fetch GauffrUser and GauffrUserExtended, GauffrCredential, informations (issues 80 & issues 81)
 - News tutorials
 - New organisation of code
 - New script usable in cronjob for prune old log (issues 14)
 - New logo (issues 79)
 - Switch API documentation to Doxygen (issues 76)

Gauffr 0.3.1
------------
 - Fix some bug in GauffrLog.

Gauffr 0.3
----------
 - Rename some methods, tables, classes...
 - Log in database instead of file (Use eZC EventLog & EventLogDatabaseTiein).
 - Use Persistent object (Use eZC PersistentObject).
 - API documentation (Use phpDocumentor).

